 For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s11301"},"text":"section 11301 of Title 42","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"priorProvisions","id":"id0cec0b60-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Prior Provisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"A prior section 1070a–24, ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/329/tIV/s404D"},"text":"Pub. L. 89–329, title IV, § 404D","children":[],"tail":", as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/325/tIV/s402/a/4"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–325, title IV, § 402(a)(4)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-07-23"},"text":"July 23, 1992","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/106/495"},"text":"106 Stat. 495","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/208/s2/b/18"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–208, § 2(b)(18)","children":[],"tail":", (19), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1993-12-20"},"text":"Dec. 20, 1993","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/107/2459"},"text":"107 Stat. 2459","children":[],"tail":", related to scholarship component, prior to the general amendment of this division by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/244"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–244","children":[],"tail":". See "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s1070a–25"},"text":"section 1070a–25 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id0cec0b61-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2008—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/315"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–315","children":[],"tail":" amended section generally. Prior to amendment, section consisted of subsecs. (a) to (d) providing for services, use of funds, priority students, and allowable providers relating to early intervention."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1999—Subsec. (c)(2). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/78"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–78","children":[],"tail":" substituted “Richard B. Russell National School Lunch Act” for “National School Lunch Act”."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
